Class Manager

java.lang.Object
shop.pos.dao.DatabaseConnection
shop.pos.dao.Manager
public class Manager extends DatabaseConnection
Represents a manager in the Point of Sale system. This class provides functionality for manager operations including menu management, inventory management, and generating various reports.
Author:
Jonah Coffelt
